You can now proudly display your photographs for the whole world to see with the Sony DPF-A710 digital photo frame. This photo frame has a 7 inch LCD display screen with a resolution of 480 x 234 dot pixels. Images can be viewed in 16:10 aspect ratio. With the LED backlight of this Sony digital picture frame, you can enjoy your images while reducing your power consumption.

The Auto Orientation sensor of this Sony DPF-A710 will automatically rotate your photos into landscape or portrait format. The Sony digital frame has 128 MB internal storage capacity in which you can save up to 250 images.

Body and Power

This Sony digital photo frame weighs 344 g and has a sleek design. The rim of the photo frame has a bezel design and gives the Sony photo frame an elegant look. The control buttons of this Sony digital picture frame are on the back panel of the body.

The Sony DPF-A710 is powered by an AC power adaptor that can function in a voltage range of 100 - 240 V. The digital frame consumes 5 watts of power. With the multiple power On/Off settings, you can also save power and have the Sony digital frame switch off automatically.

Connectivity and Features

The Sony digital picture frame lets you watch images in JPEG, TIFF, BMP and RAW file formats. External storage devices that are compatible with this DPF-A710 are memory sticks like MagicGate MS Duo and MS PRO-HG Duo. Also compatible with this Sony digital picture frame are memory cards like Mini SDHC card and Micro SDHC card and MMC like RS-MMC and MMC Plus. With the USB Mini B-type high speed port, you can also connect flash drives and your computer to the Sony digital picture frame and download or view images from them.

Images can be seen individually or in slideshow mode with creative transition effects. You can scroll through the thumbnail view to pick the images you want to see. Manual rotation of image is also possible with the Sony DPF-A710. The Sony DPF-A720 has a Clock and Calendar feature, which can display the day and date with your images, brightening up your days immeasurably.
productAttributes.title: Sony DPF-A710 7 inch Digital Photo Frame 128 MB

Life is full of small moments of joy that you try and capture so that you can sit back at a later date and recall how happy those little doses made you. This is one of the reasons that photographs are possessions which are cherished deeply by one and all, because they take them back in time to the moment when they were at their happiest and having the most fun.

Even though the value attached to them remains unchanged, from physical prints to digital copies that take up very little space and last longer, photos have come a long way. Framed graduation photos used to be the pride and joy of every household but the need for space and fast pace of lifestyle leaves little time to go into all that trouble to cherish and display such photos.

Technology has yet again come to our rescue, providing a simple, effective way of displaying your favorite photos and reminding you to value small moments even on bad days, with digital photo frames. This DigiFlip DF001 Digital Photo Frame comes with 6 inch LCD screen and can be placed in both landscape and portrait modes.

Additionally, this Digital Photo Frame from DigiFlip also comes with a calendar and clock, making it more functional than just a framed photograph. The frame also boasts of a slideshow feature and can display all your JPG images with exceptional clarity. This frame from DigiFlip consumes 3 W of power and needs a supply of 5 V, 600 mA of DC power to function as well.

The DigiFlip DF001 comes with a display resolution of 480 x 800 and a viewing area of 74.88 x 129.24 mm as well with an aspect ratio of 16:9. The Digital Photo Frame is compatible with both SDHC and SD cards up to a capacity of 32 GB, apart from an internal memory of 4 MB. Catch up with the future while you hold on to the memories of the past with this Digital Photo Frame from DigiFlip.
